{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 2",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-577256136944649201 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/223a18-2/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=577256136911094769&sectionId=577256136944649201)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","label":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","default":"7 Smart Reasons Why 40,000+ Women Are Switching to Multi-Collagen Capsules Instead of Traditional Skincare"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","label":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","default":"<p>By Rachel Beaumont | July 2025</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6uIDISuu8_text","label":"gg6uIDISuu8_text","default":"1. It’s Not Just One Collagen, It’s Five."},{"type":"html","id":"gg9mt8SYjhb_text","label":"gg9mt8SYjhb_text","default":"<p>Let’s be real—no one wants to juggle five different supplements every day. That’s why people are loving Nifora’s Multi-Collagen Capsule. It combines <strong>Types I, II, III, V, and X</strong> to support skin, joints, bones, and more—<strong>all in one easy daily dose.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4Cc7NeQu0_text","label":"gg4Cc7NeQu0_text","default":"<p>It’s especially perfect for women in their 30s, 40s, and beyond, when collagen production naturally starts to decline <strong>(yep, up to 1% less each year after 25!)</strong>. That loss can show up as wrinkles, joint stiffness, or thinning hair.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This capsule helps fill in those gaps—<strong>so you can feel as strong, radiant, and confident as ever.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsLvG4OII__text","label":"ggsLvG4OII__text","default":"2. Your Skin Doesn’t Just Need Moisture. It Needs Structure."},{"type":"html","id":"ggEJn8C1uIW_text","label":"ggEJn8C1uIW_text","default":"<p>I used to think dryness and sagging just meant I needed a richer moisturizer. But turns out, it goes way deeper than that. As we age, our skin’s support system—<strong>collagen</strong>—starts breaking down. And no cream can fix that from the outside.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggI2ohkC2hm_text","label":"ggI2ohkC2hm_text","default":"<p>That’s why I started taking collagen supplements, and honestly, <strong>it made a huge difference.</strong> It’s not just about that glow (though that’s a bonus!)—<strong>it’s about rebuilding the foundation so your skin stays strong, plump, and bouncy for the long haul.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg26i4zU6M9_text","label":"gg26i4zU6M9_text","default":"3. Menopause Changes Everything and Your Routine Should Too."},{"type":"html","id":"ggsxyDLVOcJ_text","label":"ggsxyDLVOcJ_text","default":"<p>No one really warned me <strong>how much hormones could affect my skin and joints</strong>—until I started feeling it. When estrogen dips, collagen takes a hit too, and suddenly things feel thinner, stiffer, and just… off.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg96ugxQo9g_text","label":"gg96ugxQo9g_text","default":"<p>That’s why I’m so glad <strong>this formula doesn’t just stop at collagen.</strong> It also includes hormone-supportive ingredients like magnesium and biotin, which help my body adjust instead of fight the changes. It’s not about stopping menopause—<strong>it’s about working&nbsp;with it and still feeling strong, glowy, and like myself.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggntnhoAX_p_text","label":"ggntnhoAX_p_text","default":"4. It Includes Ingredients That Help Collagen Work."},{"type":"html","id":"ggAnsGbE4zn_text","label":"ggAnsGbE4zn_text","default":"<p>Here’s the thing: <strong>collagen doesn’t work solo</strong>. That’s why this capsule includes essentials like vitamin C <strong>(which helps your body actually&nbsp;make collagen)</strong>, plus keratin and biotin to support strong hair, nails, and smoother skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg59Q6qkpGD_text","label":"gg59Q6qkpGD_text","default":"<p>Most formulas skip these, <strong>but this one covers all the bases.</strong> When the body gets everything it needs—not just one piece of the puzzle—<strong>you really start to see the difference.</strong> Think of it like giving your skin a full renovation, not just a quick fix.</p>"}],
